    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Honest, budget-friendly transportation with plenty of value for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered in as-is condition and is best suited for someone looking for an affordable project, backup car, or basic daily driver with room to improve. A straightforward opportunity to get into a vehicle at an accessible price from a seller focused on clear, transparent representation.",
