    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable runabout or a handy little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants simple, usable transport without spending a fortune. It has the usual wear you\u2019d expect at this stage, but it still has plenty of potential and could make a great first car, spare vehicle, or practical get-around. If you\u2019re after something cheap, honest, and ready to find a new home, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or dependable beater with a strong-running drivetrain, responsive steering, and the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes ownership straightforward. Not a showroom car and it shows cosmetic wear, but it still presents as a usable platform with good bones for someone who wants an affordable daily, shop runabout, or weekend fixer-upper. Starts, moves, and offers plenty of value for a hands-on buyer looking for practical transportation with enthusiast potential.",
      "price": 7900.0,
