    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014honest, seasoned, and full of possibility. It\u2019s the sort of ride that feels right at home in the hands of someone who appreciates a machine with a story, whether you\u2019re after a budget-friendly runabout, a practical backup vehicle, or a project with real personality. There\u2019s a gritty charm here that makes every trip feel a little more interesting, and for the right buyer, it\u2019s an opportunity to get into something memorable without spending a fortune.",
      "price": 6900.0,
