      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation, a project, or a handy extra vehicle. It shows its age and would love a little TLC, but that\u2019s exactly what makes it such a great value. Priced to sell and represented honestly by a seller who believes in being straightforward and easy to deal with.",
